snippet.title: Nivalis - Official Announcement Trailer (4K 60fps)
snippet.description:
Welcome to Nivalis, the city that stretches from the ocean to the clouds.
Grow your business, manage restaurants and nightclubs, make friends and enemies, buy and decorate apartments, go fishing and maybe even find love.
